author: Joseph Duarte
title: UH's top recruit Bryan Jones: 'I'm going to destroy this conference'
text:
Photo: David Becker, AP Photo UH's top recruit Bryan Jones: 'I'm going to destroy this conference' 1 / 1 Back to Gallery 
The University of Houston's highest-rated recruit is in: Baton Rouge (La.) Madison Prep Academy defensive end Bryan Jones has sent in his national letter of intent. 
Jones, who is ranked No. 170 on the ESPN300 list of top national recruits, was a late pickup for the Cougars. He chose UH over Texas A&M.
